Description:
    Generates a new Me Salva! customized serializer at app/serializers.
    Pass the serializer name as an argument, either CamelCased or snake_cased.
    It is possible to pass the attributes arguments as well.

Example:
    `bin/rails generate ms_serializer Awesome`
    `bin/rails generate ms_serializer Awesome attribute1:string attribute2:integer attribute3:references`

    creates a Me Salva! customized awesome serializer:
        app/serializers/awesome_serializer.rb
